Chinese President Xi Jinping delivered a keynote speech via video at the opening ceremony of the Boao Forum for Asia Annual Conference 2022 on Thursday. He said that the world should seize opportunities to foster a more open Asia-wide market and make new strides in mutually beneficial cooperation. In this episode of BizBeat, CGTN's Zhu Zhu explains that Asia not only contributed to global economic growth but also showed the world its wisdom in regional governance.